          "tz": 480
        },
        "subject": "LU-812 llite: 3.0+ kernel fsync should call write",
        "message": "LU-812 llite: 3.0+ kernel fsync should call write\n\nSince 3.0, kernel pushes i_mutex and fsync to fs fsync\ncallback. So Lustre should check and do the same. Otherwise\nthere might be data corruption and sanity 63b will fail.\n\nSigned-off-by: Peng Tao <tao.peng@emc.com>\nChange-Id: I2f2f6792276eaf6783bffb813f3c3e5405be0450\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
  },
